{"tid":2355004,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"麵咪媽真係一代股神","createTime":"2021-01-06T01:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T01:29:48.000Z","uid":81236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"33479ac9f47105ab97733a4bd2c179b2bc369ee5","tid":2355004,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:22:30.000Z","msg":"再中埋700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底美團最後既死法係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普簽行政命令禁支付寶等多個中國應用程式交易<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普簽署行政命令，禁止與碼蟻集團旗下支付寶等中國應用程式進行交易。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，被禁的8個中國應用程式，包括支付寶、<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">QQ錢包和微信</span></span>支付等，行政命令要求商務部，確定哪些交易將被禁止。<br />\n<br />\n官員說，中國應用程式擁有龐大的用戶群，有機會讀取敏感數據，做法是要遏止程式對美國人構成的威脅。商務部有45天時間採取行動，但當局計劃在特朗普今個月20日卸任前，識別出需要禁止的交易。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568853-20210106.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568853-20210106.htm&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=671bc17a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568853-20210106.htm&h=7be27cf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568853-20210106.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0a614e7e8ebbfa8728b1ca6313ae33b954c410ae","tid":2355004,"uid":44462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:23:32.000Z","msg":"係未來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e93fa1cfe07b32e077eea2f1aea53a171690af1","tid":2355004,"uid":59357,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:25:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35fd4cfa9aa56ef1d838895a794be31d153b839d","tid":2355004,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e93fa1cfe07b32e077eea